    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey everyone! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, it is in incredible shape! It\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014always garage-kept and detailed regularly. It looks and drives just like it did the day I bought it. If you\u2019re looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it! Come see it for yourself and you'll see exactly what I mean!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
