      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with its signature 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This specimen retains its mechanical purity with a factory ZF 6-speed manual transmission and a perfectly dialed variable M differential lock. The chassis is impeccable, with documented subframe reinforcement and a recently overhauled VANOS system ensuring optimal cam timing. Performance is sharp thanks to fresh bushings and a pristine suspension geometry that delivers telepathic steering feedback. This is a turn-key example for the discerning collector who demands peak atmospheric performance and structural integrity.",
